text: Therese Olausson (born 13 January 1968) is a Swedish equestrian. She competed in the team eventing at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Sweden Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Borås
